<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-rbsA2VBKQhggwzxH7pPCaAqO46MgnOM80zW1RWuH61DGLwZJEdK2Kadq2F9CUG65" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/tc_details.css">
</head>
<body >
    <div id="tc-body">
        <input type="text" value="<%=student.FirstName%> <%=student.LastName%>" id="student_name" hidden>
    <input type="text" value="<%=student.AdmissionNo%>" id="admno" hidden>
    <div class="certificate">
        <div class="school-name">
                <img width="100%" src="/images/school-header.png" alt="" srcset="">
         </div>
		 <h2>Transfer Certificate</h2>
         <%if(err){%>
            <h3 style="color: red;"><%=err%></h3>
        <%}else{%>
            
        
         
        <div class="date">Date of Issuance: <%=tcData.RelievingDate%></div>
		<div class="date">TC Number: Number</div>
		<div class="date">Admission No:<%=student.AdmissionNo%></div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>To Whom It May Concern,</p>

<p>
This is to certify that <b> <%=student.FirstName%> <%=student.LastName%> </b>father's name <b> <%=student.FathersName%> </b> mother's name <b> <%=student.MothersName%> </b> religion <%=student.Religion%>
                caste <%=student.Caste%> attended Shree Veer Vidya Niketan School Shahpur from <%=tcData.AdmissionDate%> to <%=tcData.RelievingDate%> and now leaves on <%=tcData.RelievingDate%> paying all fees.
</p>


<p>
His/Her date of birth as per school record was <%=DOBDate%> and in words <%=DOBInWords%>.
</p>


<p>
The last promotion examination appeared by him/her was <%=tcData.RelievingClass%> in the year <%=student.Session + 1%> and his/her result was <%=student.TotalGrade%>.
</p>


<p>
He/She was enrolled in class <%=tcData.AdmissionClass%> , He/She has been vaccinated or is otherwise protected from small pox.
                His/Her conduct was CONDUCT and leaves the school on account of <%=tcData.RelievingClass%>.
</p>


<p>


</p>
<br/>
<br/>
<br/>
        </div>
        <div class="signature">Principal's Signature: ______________________</div>
        <%}%>
    </div>

    </div>
    
    
</body>
<div style="position: fixed;top: 2%;right: 3%;">
    <button id="tc-download" class="btn btn-warning">Download</button>
</div>
<script src="/js/pdfCreator.js"></script>
<script src="/js/tcdetails.js"></script>
